{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bbf324fb62","title":"中央军委转发毛泽东、林彪同意南京军区党委紧急请示中的三条意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1ade9a12b2","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"bbf324fb62"}],"tags":[{"id":"46426acff1","name":"中共中央转发","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6d68f4fe50","type":"title","text":"中央军委转发毛泽东、林彪同意南京军区党委紧急请示中的三条意见","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62"},{"id":"b6242c2697","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、林副主席同意南京军区党委十二月一日来电中所提的三条意见，批示通报全国同样照办。现将南京军区党委的原电转发你们，望遵照执行，并请转告各中央局、各省市委。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62"},{"id":"638568ae1a","type":"paragraph","text":"南京军区党委三条意见","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62"},{"id":"272ec4141d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一切转业、复员军人不准成立红卫军或其他名义的单独组织，只应参加所在单位的文化革命组织。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62"},{"id":"1aa320cd40","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）不准许冲进解放军机关及所属部队，也不许到部队串联和散发传单。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62"},{"id":"845ab75fbd","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）所有转业、复员军人，必须保持和发扬解放军的光荣传统，并协助解放军加强战备，保卫无产阶级文化大革命。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62"},{"id":"0e314e5792","type":"paragraph","text":"南京军区党委","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62"},{"id":"b848fdef04","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年十二月一日","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62"}],"page":{"id":"d4e8279ca0","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"bbf324fb62","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}